Hey guys!
I’ve recently teamed up with @heybudskincare who sent me a clay mask. 
After using the mask my skin felt smoother and brighter and after a couple days some of my acne had started to clear. 
Acne is something I’ve struggled with my entire life especially during stressful periods of my life. I’ve tried so many different products on my skin and the reaction to those products has been different each time. 
These products are ones I can highly recommend
